    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《士兵大战僵尸》是一款塔防游戏，僵尸已经席卷世界，人类最后的希望寄托在精英士兵身上。从激光步枪到死亡机关枪，你将部署部队并使用特殊技能阻止变异僵尸的进攻浪潮！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/bf77936c51a2437ece740c2a0943aaf9.webp?t=1772361266\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/dc67e32627b4cf4de9baff59375d2d15.poster.avif?t=1772361266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/dc67e32627b4cf4de9baff59375d2d15.webm?t=1772361266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/dc67e32627b4cf4de9baff59375d2d15.mp4?t=1772361266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《士兵大战僵尸》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《士兵大战僵尸》是一款快节奏塔防游戏，背景设定在被僵尸占领的世界中。指挥装备有激光步枪和死亡机关枪的精英士兵，阻止变异僵尸的进攻。每名士兵都有独特技能，你可以升级他们的属性以应对越来越艰难的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/94daaa20409b1fb23c3322fa6ee6aca9.webp?t=1772361266\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/e833857fd71eeb4a27c9b51dacdacc45.poster.avif?t=1772361266\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/e833857fd71eeb4a27c9b51dacdacc45.webm?t=1772361266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307010/extras/e833857fd71eeb4a27c9b51dacdacc45.mp4?t=1772361266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过40个关卡、多种僵尸类型和多样技能，需要策略思考才能生存。使用士兵的能力和强大武器，阻止人类灭绝，体验充满动作的策略防御乐趣。</p>",
